        "TileImage": "$($repository 92478768-9a59-4148-9afa-b27c6bbf63e0).Image",
        "Description": "Ah Agent 47,\r\rwelcome to New York again!\rThe coffee is burnt, the stock market is crushed and the map where to find the right office is outdated.\r\rBut hey, we know the struggle already from other maps. So don&#39;t cry, stop raging and get your stuff together. Gidget needs and accident to get some time off, Athena needs a cut, Lewis &quot;Oooopsie&quot; Thomas needs a relief and Edgar, well Edgar is simply Edgar.\r\rTime to give some extra spice to the Wall Street.\r\rCheers,\r\rBbbbbburgers",
